title: Megacity 909
description:
Megacity is set in a near dystopic future where a global war led to the pacification of society by the insertion of a computer chip. However, just as world peace seemed within the grasp of man, a new species of ghostly parasitic creatures appeared and began attacking humans. Dubbed "pulses", the world fought back by forming a strike team of commandos called Phobia. These heroes combat the threat of the pulses and try to safeguard the planet from future attacks.

Written by Andrew Dabb and illustrated by Kano Kang and Zack Suh. Published by Devils Due.


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
